AN ACT making an appropriation to the Nevada Center for Civic Engagement to
support civics education programs in elementary, junior high, middle
and high schools in this State and to expand civics education programs
for adults; and providing other matters properly relating thereto.
THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF NEVADA, REPRESENTED IN
SENATE AND ASSEMBLY, DO ENACT AS FOLLOWS:
1 Section 1. 1. There is hereby appropriated from the State General Fund to
2 the Nevada Center for Civic Engagement [the sum of $800,000 to support] for the
3 purpose of supporting civics education programs, including, without limitation,
4 National History Day, Civics in Action Summit, KidsVention and We the People:
5 The Citizen and the Constitution Program, in Nevada’s elementary, junior high,
6 middle and high schools and to expand civics education programs for adults [.] , the
7 following sums:
8 For the Fiscal Year 2025-2026 ..................................................... $250,000
9 For the Fiscal Year 2026-2027 ..................................................... $250,000
10 2. [Of the sum appropriated by subsection 1, the Nevada Center for Civic
11 Engagement shall not expend more than $400,000 in Fiscal Year 2025-2026.
12 3.] Upon acceptance of the money appropriated by subsection 1, the Nevada
13 Center for Civic Engagement agrees to:
14 (a) Prepare and transmit a report to the Interim Finance Committee on or
15 before December 18, 2026, that describes each expenditure made from the money
16 appropriated by subsection 1 from the date on which the money was received by the
17 Nevada Center for Civic Engagement through December 1, 2026;
18 (b) Prepare and transmit a final report to the Interim Finance Committee on or
19 before September 17, 2027, that describes each expenditure made from the money
20 appropriated by subsection 1 from the date on which the money was received by the
21 Nevada Center for Civic Engagement through June 30, 2027; and
22 (c) Upon request of the Legislative Commission, make available to the
23 Legislative Auditor any of the books, accounts, claims, reports, vouchers or other

